t_id=http%3A%2F%2Feric.ed.gov%2F%3Fid%3DED459656&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABias+incident\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Community Relations Service. pg. 19.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Colton, Emma (September 4, 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dailycaller.com/2014/09/04/university-squelches-freedom-of-speech-with-campus-wide-discrimination-initiative/\">\"University Squelches Freedom Of Speech With Campus-Wide Discrimination Initiative\"</a>. <i>The Daily Caller</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">March 22,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Daily+Caller&amp;rft.atitle=University+Squelches+Freedom+Of+Speech+With+Campus-Wide+Discrimination+Initiative&amp;rft.date=2014-09-04&amp;rft.aulast=Colton&amp;rft.aufirst=Emma&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdailycaller.com%2F2014%2F09%2F04%2Funiversity-squelches-freedom-of-speech-with-campus-wide-discrimination-initiative%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABias+incident\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Community Relations Service. pg. 13.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Wessler &amp; Moss. pp. 11\u201313.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9